          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Separator after motto -->
        <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mb-8"></div>
        
        <!-- Two column layout -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative">
          <!-- Left column -->
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-3">
            <p class="text-base text-white font-medium">
              Redazione EduNews24.it
            </p>
            <p>
              Universo S.r.l. ©2022-{new Date().getFullYear()}. Tutti i diritti riservati.
            </p>
            <p>
              P.IVA. 03930330794, Via del Tritone 132, 00187 Roma
            </p>
            <p>
              Depositata al Tribunale di Lamezia Terme(CZ) - Prot.llo 189/2025 in data 3 Marzo 2025.
            </p>
            <p>
              Iscrizione ROC Pratica n° 1436921 - Direttore Responsabile: Dott. Torchia Antonello | <a href="/privacy" class="text-white underline hover:text-gray-200">Privacy</a> | <a href="/chi-siamo" class="text-white underline hover:text-gray-200">Chi Siamo</a> | <a href="/termini-di-servizio" class="text-white underline hover:text-gray-200">Termini di Servizio</a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Vertical separator between columns -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gray-700"></div>

          <!-- Right column -->
          <div class="text-sm md:text-right">
            <div class="mb-8">
              <p class="text-white font-medium">Universo S.r.l.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Redazione EduNews24.it</p>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Email: redazione@edunews24.it</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Social Media Icons -->
            <div class="flex md:justify-end gap-4">
              <a href="#" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
